{"tid":18900,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和LIHKG接軌","createTime":"2016-12-02T13:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T01:11:08.000Z","uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b3a163944a089c1f48b47a2a09a7cae18fe728","tid":18900,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和LIHKG接軌 <br />\n註冊後要拼盡全力 出post，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 netvigator email進場,先拿AC。 <br />\n然後一邊出post一邊拿Master (學校email)，以最快速度開分身打手。 <br />\n成功奪取台主身份，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(開蘿莉台，會員自貼區，引入5P文化)<br />\n<br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管論壇各個台。 <br />\n又要負責幫論壇和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。 <br />\n表現好的話可以入Admin。 <br />\n簡直是論壇主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"bc1aab8a18e627266ae55e92e990ce227b06e23f","tid":18900,"uid":21715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4ffdc9e71de0dcaa99d482806e7cb1adc4572343","tid":18900,"uid":30653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:41:01.000Z","msg":"幽默感依加野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ba571d17e8c4fff53c4d7e49abdaca3b31a886","tid":18900,"uid":17109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"6分 幾好笑"},{"pid":"d30611223423de9f5df3e141eb454d1c4b7b4598","tid":18900,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"跑咗一萬米手臂好粗"},{"pid":"abc39e15cd6a9d1cb91a82988b2394b115e07443","tid":18900,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"下一站金鐘&hellip;the next station is....."},{"pid":"9eb9e16339c04ddf1248223abea98bb21de0394b","tid":18900,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma